name: 10.7 Kw Smart Energy Storage Battery Pack
description:
Main Features
1. 120A MPPT solar charger inside, max pv input 6kw+ (27A )                                                                                                                                                

2. With local wifi built inside (Requires App. Remote Wifi optional)                                                                                                                                                                          

3. USB on-the-go function                                                                                                                                                                                      

4. Optional for parallel operation up to 9 units 

5. User programmable RGB lighting for different operation mode.
6. Smart battery management.Compitable with different types of batteries:Lead acid, AGM, Gel, flooded, tubular,LiFePo4                                                                                             

7. On grid and Off Grid Solar Inverter, support self-consumption and feed into the grid.                                                                                                                                                

8. Various communication such as USB/RS232/RS485/dry contact/WIFI/ optional.                                                                                                                                   

9. Touch buttons on LCD display                                                                                                                                                                                                                          

10. Wide PV input range (Up to 500Vdc), support no battery working during the day time.
